NAME

    Device::L3GD20 - I2C interface to L3GD20 3 axis GyroScope using
    Device::SMBus

VERSION

    version 0.010

ATTRIBUTES

 I2CBusDevicePath

    this is the device file path for your I2CBus that the L3GD20 is
    connected on e.g. /dev/i2c-1 This must be provided during object
    creation.

 Gyroscope

        $self->Gyroscope->enable();
        $self->Gyroscope->getReading();

    This is a object of Device::Gyroscope::L3GD20

SUPPORT

 Bugs / Feature Requests

    Please report any bugs or feature requests through github at
